MF= 3 Neutron cross sections                                      9915 1451
  Below 0.3 eV:                                                   9915 1451
    The fission cross section at 0.0253 eV was assumed to be 2000 9915 1451
    b which is almost the same as Es-254 fission cross section.   9915 1451
    The capture cross section at 0.0253 eV was assumed to be 250  9915 1451
    b from the fission cross section at 0.0253 eV and capture to  9915 1451
    fission ratio at 1 eV calculated with CCONE code/7/.          9915 1451
    The elastic scattering cross section of 9.4 b was calculated  9915 1451
    from scattering radius of 8.628 fm/7/.                        9915 1451
                                                                  9915 1451
  Above 0.3 eV:                                                   9915 1451
    Cross sections calculated with CCONE code/7/ were adopted.    9915 1451
    The same parameters as those for Es-254 were used in the      9915 1451
    CCONE calculation.                                            9915 1451
